window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Are you anxious and not sure why?</p> <p>If you answer yes, then that’s completely normal; you are human! Our brains aren’t evolved for the complexities and complications of modern life.</p> <p>So for his next trick, Derren Brown will reboot your brain, with the help of world-renowned experts. By drawing on wisdom and insights from modern psychology to ancient philosophy, Derren demonstrates how you can rise above your brain’s limitations and think yourself into a more fulfilling, less anxiety-ridden and perhaps happier life.&nbsp;</p> <p>A 7digital production for Audible Original Podcasts.</p>"; 
